prompts.frontCover:
Greeting card front cover featuring Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo, reimagined as comic book superheroes in a dynamic and funny scene. The style is classic comic book art with bold outlines, vibrant colors, Ben-Day dots for shading, and exaggerated action.

The scene is set on a stylized San Diego beach, with iconic piers and palm trees in the background under a bright blue sky.

In the foreground, "Boba Girl" (Lao Lao) and "Beach Boy" (Jordan) strike a heroic, back-to-back action pose. Lao Lao, on the left, is illustrated in her blue sweatshirt and black pants. She winks playfully at the viewer while expertly dual-wielding oversized boba tea drinks like weapons, with tapioca pearls flying out like ammunition in a cool, slow-motion effect. Jordan, on the right, is in his brown hoodie and dark pants. He has a confident, heroic smile and is holding a surfboard under one arm, posing as if ready to charge into the waves.

The entire composition is framed within a dynamic comic book panel. Fun, explosive sound effect graphics like "BWOOSH!" and "POP!" surround the flying boba pearls. The overall tone is action-packed, silly, and heroic.

Centered in the middle of the card, layered over the characters, is the text "Happy Birthday to my Favorite Superhero, Lao Lao!" in a beautiful, readable, and slightly playful handwritten cursive script. The text color contrasts brightly against the background for easy readability.
